{
  "doc_id": "12054",
  "text": "Binary vector constructs were transformed into Agrobacterium tumefaciens strain LBA4404 by electroporation. Transformed agrobacteria were confirmed by colony PCR, and the constructs transformed into N. tabacum cv. Xanthi NN leaf discs as previously described [CITATION_1] . T1 transformants were selected on MS media containing kanamycin, and the kanamycin resistant plantlets were transferred to soil after 14 days.",
